---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import HeroImg from "../components/HeroImg.astro";
import heroImg from "../images/index/wedded-hero.webp";
---

<Layout>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found | Wedded</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Oops! This page doesn’t exist. Maybe try going back to the homepage or exploring our blog content."
    />
    <meta property="og:title" content="404 - Page Not Found | Wedded" />
    <meta
      property="og:description"
      content="Oops! This page doesn’t exist. Maybe try going back to the homepage or exploring our blog content."
    />
    <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://weddedpod.com/404" />
    <meta property="og:image" content="/images/index/wedded-hero.webp" />
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="404 - Page Not Found | Wedded" />
    <meta
      name="twitter:description"
      content="Oops! This page doesn’t exist. Maybe try going back to the homepage or exploring our podcast and blog content."
    />
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="/images/index/wedded-hero.webp" />
    <link
      rel="preload"
      as="image"
      href={heroImg.src}
      type="image/webp"
      fetchpriority="high"
    />
  </Fragment>
  <HeroImg title="OH NO!" background={heroImg} />
  <main>
    <div class="content-container">
      <div class="privacy-wrapper">
        <section>
          <h1>404 – Page Not Found</h1>
        </section>
        <section>
          <p>
            Well this is just outright embarrassing. I don't know if it's more
            embarrassing for you or more embarrassing for us.
          </p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <p>
            You somehow navigated to a non-existent page. If you're certain that
            we should be embarrassed, then send us an email at <a
              href="mailto:weddedpod@gmail.com?subject=Oh%20No&body=I%20noticed%20this%20mistake:"
              >weddedpod@gmail.com</a
            >
          </p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <p>
            If you think this is your mistake, and not ours... then hang your
            head and return to the homepage, like a coward.
          </p>
        </section>
        <section>
          <a href="/"> Return to homepage </a>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
